<html>
<head>
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <div>[FirstName]!</div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div>Here is a receipt of your booking changes, ticket info and check-in instructions.</div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="position:relative;width: 100%;height: 190px;background:url([ImageUrl]) no-repeat center center;">
        <div style="text-align: center;margin-bottom:15px;padding-top:18px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;">[Hotel_Name]</span></div>

        <div style="text-align: center;margin-bottom:10px;"><span style="color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;">[Neighborhood]</span></div>

        <div style="text-align: center;margin-top:5px;">[rating]</div>

        <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;"><a href="[UrlViewDayPass]" style="background-color:#13c1f4;font-size:20px;text-tranform:uppercase;color:#FFF;text-decoration:none;width:200px;height:48px;line-height:48px;display:inline-block;">VIEW TICKET</a></div>
    </div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">[Address]</div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">[AddressInfo]</div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">[PhoneNumber]</div>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <h2>Mobile Only Check-In</h2>
    </div>

    <ul>
        <li>Go to your email confirmation on your mobile phone</li>
        <li>Tap <strong><a href="[UrlViewDayPass]">VIEW TICKET</a></strong> button</li>
        <li>Show your ticket and your photo ID to the <b>[CheckInPlace]</b> who will validate.</li>
    </ul>

    <div>&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <h2>Receipt Details</h2>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</div>

    <table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="15" style="width:100%; background-color: #F6F6F6;">
        <tbody>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right; width:45%;">Guest Name:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[FullName]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Booked:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[BookedDate]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Booking Id:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[BookingCode]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Check-In Date:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[CheckInDate] <a href="[UrlViewDayPass]" style="background-color:#13c1f4;font-size:12px;text-tranform:uppercase;color:#FFF;text-decoration:none;width:84px;height:32px;line-height:32px;display:inline-block;text-align:center;">[CheckInText]</a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
            <td style="color: #9b9b9b;font-size: 10px;font-weight: bold;">Must be selected prior to arrival. Same day check-in is available, subject to daily availability.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Original Ticket Price:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left: 7px;">[OriginalPerTicketPrice]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">New Ticket Price:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[PerTicketPrice]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Max Per Ticket:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left: 7px;">[MaxGuest]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Tickets:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left: 7px;">[Tickets]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Total Difference:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left: 7px;">[BookingTotalDifference]</td>
        </tr>
        [Discount]
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: right;">Total:</td>
            <td style="text-align: left; padding-left:7px;">[BookingTotal]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="visibility: [FinePrintVisible];">
            <td colspan="2">
                <h4 style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px;margin: 0 auto 15px;">FINE PRINT</h4>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="visibility: [FinePrintVisible];">
            <td colspan="2">
                <ul class="fine-print" style="margin-left:40px;margin-right:20px;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:10px;">
                    <li>Check-in date must be selected prior to arrival (same day selection is available, subject to daily availability)</li>
                    <li>Check-in date can be changed at no charge anytime 48 hours or more before check-in</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="2" style="text-align: center;">For more information please see <a href="[UrlLinkToTerms]">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>.</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:10px;">&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align:center;"><strong>Thanks again for booking</strong></div>

    <div style="text-align:center;">Have fun</div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:10px;">&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 5px;"><a href="[UrlViewDayPass]" style="background-color: #13c1f4; font-size: 20px; text-tranform: uppercase; color: #FFF; text-decoration: none; width: 200px; height: 48px; line-height: 48px; display: inline-block;">[ViewDayPassString]</a></div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;">&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;">&nbsp;</div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;">
        <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;">Revise your booking or report trouble with your booking. Please email us at <a href="mailto:help@dayaxe.com">help@dayaxe.com</a></div>

    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:5px;">&nbsp;</div>
</body>
</html>
